.name
Watcher
.author
Franz Hemmer 
.version
V37
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A little title-bar commodity which can be customized to show various
information such as the free space on hard drive partitions, free memory,
system time and date etc.  Font and Overscan sensitive, can jump between
public screens by clicking on it's Zoom gadget.  Includes WatcherPrefs, a
utility that allows you to customize what Watcher displays and its general
behavior.  
